These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, rose, iris, daisy
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, writer
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, august, april, october
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, frog, rabbit
1. the photographer is the person who growsdaffodil##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is the designer##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the photographer##1
5. the scientist is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the photographer is the owner of the cat##1
8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Flower         | daffodil  | daisy  | rose | iris |
| Job           | photographer | designer | writer  | scientist  |
| Birthday   | october       | april      | march | august      |
| Pet           | cat          | fish     | frog    | rabbit     |

