.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, kiwi, orange, papaya
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, mystery, horror, disaster
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, chef, paramedic, journalist
1. the person eating broccoli is on the far right##1
2. the person watching disaster movies is the police-officer##1
3. the person eating orange is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the paramedic is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
6. the person drinking sprite is the person watching horror movies##1
7. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the paramedic is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
9. the police-officer is on the right of the journalist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | cola       | iced-tea | tea        |
| Food          | papaya     | kiwi       | orange   | broccoli   |
| Movie-Genre   | horror      | mystery       | disaster     | comedy    |
| Job         | paramedic | journalist | police-officer | chef |

