.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, security-guard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, february, march, april
City: berlin, san-francisco, venice, edinburgh
 1. the person drinking tea is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the electrician##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | 7up       | tea        | mirinda        |
| Job           | electrician   | librarian | designer   | security-guard |
| Birthday   | january     | february    | april | march        |
| City           | venice         | berlin  | edinburgh       | san-francisco         |

