.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, white, emerald, fuchsia
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, d&b, electronic, funk
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, camping, fishing, baking
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, guinea-pig, horse
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the far right##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
5. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
6. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who likes white##1
7. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
8. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Color           | white   | ivory  | fuchsia | emerald |
| Music-Genre   | electronic | funk       | d&b       | ambient     |
| Hobby   | fishing       | baking    | camping     | video-games  |
| Pet           | ferret     | guinea-pig | horse     | cat         |

