2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
4. the indian is on the left of the french##1
5. the turkish is on the right of the person playing domino##1
6. the person playing domino is the thai##1
7. the french is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the social-worker is on the right of the person driving the train##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | analyst  | teacher    | social-worker | videographer |
| Transport   | boat      | train    | taxi         | jet-ski    |
| Nationality   | indian   | french     | thai          | turkish      |
| Game         | billiard | mah-jongg | domino      | poker      |

