.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, blend, vegafina, game
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, tulip, aconite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, scientific, thriller
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, horse, mouse
 1. the vegafina-smoker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 2. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who growsbellflower is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the owner of the horse is the tiparillo-smoker##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who growsaconite##1
 6. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person who growstulip is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the fish is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | tiparillo  | game | vegafina     | blend |
| Flower           | tulip  | aconite      | bellflower | iris    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | scientific  | fantasy    | thriller  |
| Pet           | horse   | mouse       | fish       | frog      |

