.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, december, march, october
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, sudoku, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, r&b, blues, folk
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, scooter, taxi
 1. the fan of techno is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the fan of folk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the fan of techno is the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday    | june | december     | march    | october |
| Hobby       | baking | sudoku    | woodworking | cooking |
| Music-Genre         | r&b   | blues  | folk        | techno    |
| Transport   | taxi   | quad-bike | airplane    | scooter |

