5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person who growslily##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
7. the freelancer is the gothic-revival house##1
8. the palace house is the person who growslily##1
9. the ranch-style house is the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
