5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
7. the person driving the snowmobile is the person eating peach##1
8. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
9. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | video-games | baking     |
| Beverage   | coffee   | milk       | mirinda       | hot-chocolate  |
| Food           | lemon    | blueberry    | broccoli       | peach       |
