 7. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 9. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the person eating garlic is the person who likes turquise##1

.:: Answer ::.
